OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBoy's family appalled at   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FGatwick wheelchair wait    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An eight-year-old boy who has had both 
OL,6, legs amputated was forced to wait hours
OL,7, for his wheelchair to be returned at   
OL,8, Gatwick Airport.                       
OL,10,FPaula Hudgell said she was "appalled"  
OL,11,Fthat no help was offered after her son 
OL,12,FTony was left stranded at 03:00 GMT.   
OL,14,FTony lost his limbs following abuse by 
OL,15,Fhis birth parents, who were jailed for 
OL,16,F10 years in 2018.                      
OL,18,FGatwick Airport has apologised for the 
OL,19,Fdistress caused but said it experienced
OL,20,Fsignificant disruption on Sunday night.
